PN,31001
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer is set to announce
OL,7,Fsweeping reforms to protect children
OL,8,Fonline at a Downing Street press
OL,9,Fconference on Monday ` vowing to "call
OL,10,Ftime on a system that's failing our
OL,11,Fkids".
OL,13,FThe prime minister is expected to
OL,14,Ffollow Australia's example by
OL,15,Fintroducing a social media ban for
OL,16,Funder-16s, including TikTok,
OL,17,FInstagram, Threads, Facebook, X,
OL,18,FYouTube, Snapchat and Reddit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FHowever, the ban will go further than
OL,7,FAustralia's by including romantic or
OL,8,Fsexual AI chatbots, and children could
OL,9,Falso be blocked from chatting to
OL,10,Fstrangers on gaming platforms,
OL,11,Faccording to The Sunday Times.
OL,13,FThe newspaper reported that daily
OL,14,Fsocial media use will be limited for
OL,15,Funder-18s in a bid to stop late-night
OL,16,Fscrolling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FStarmer promised "bold action" in
OL,7,Fresponse to calls for change from
OL,8,Fparents, after the vast majority
OL,9,Fresponding to the government
OL,10,Fconsultation backed a minimum age of
OL,11,F16 before children can access social
OL,12,Fmedia platforms.
OL,14,FThe public consultation on the issue,
OL,15,Fwhich closed on May 26, received about
OL,16,F116,000 responses, making it the
OL,17,Fsecond-largest in history.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31004
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FOver 83% of parents who responded said
OL,7,Fsocial media risks outweigh the
OL,8,Fbenefits for children ` with 91%
OL,9,Fbacking a minimum age of 16 before
OL,10,Fplatforms can offer their services to
OL,11,Fchildren.
OL,13,FAlmost two thirds (62%) of children
OL,14,Fwho responded said restricting the
OL,15,Fhigh-risk features would make them
OL,16,Fsafer online. But 72% also said they
OL,17,Fwere worried about feeling left out if
OL,18,Frestrictions came in.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31005
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,F"How we keep kids safe online is one
OL,7,Fof the biggest debates of our time. As
OL,8,Fa dad, I know every parent wants their
OL,9,Fchild to grow up safe and happy," the
OL,10,Fprime minister said.
OL,12,F"This is a choice about whose side
OL,13,Fwe're on: families across the country,
OL,14,For a status quo that isn't working.
OL,15,FPeople rightly expect action, and this
OL,16,FGovernment will always stand up for
OL,17,Fparents and put children first.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31006
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,F"That's why we will call time on a
OL,7,Fsystem that's failing our kids and
OL,8,Ftake bold action to give every child
OL,9,Fthe best possible start in life."
OL,11,FIt comes after Starmer last week
OL,12,Fissued a three-month ultimatum to
OL,13,FApple and Google to make it
OL,14,Ftechnologically impossible for
OL,15,Fchildren to take, share or view nude
OL,16,Fimages on their smartphones.
OL,18,FThe latest move risks prompting a
OL,19,Fbacklash from Donald Trump's pro-tech
OL,20,FUS administration, which warned
OL,21,Fagainst a blanket ban for under-16s.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FIn a response to the consultation, the
OL,7,FUS embassy in London said the country
OL,8,Fpreferred "narrowly targeted
OL,9,Frequirements", that "most content
OL,10,Fshould be accessible by default", and
OL,11,Fthat age verification requirements
OL,12,Fcould "impose disproportionate
OL,13,Fcompliance burdens on American
OL,14,Fcompanies".
OL,16,FThe reforms come at a difficult time
OL,17,Ffor Starmer's premiership, which has
OL,18,Fbeen under pressure since Labour's
OL,19,Fdrubbing in May's local and devolved
OL,20,Felections.
OL,26,@pD@KOUqD@MO]qD@UOUrD@`O]tD@GOUvD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31008
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FHis authority was dealt a further blow
OL,7,Flast week by the resignations of the
OL,8,Fdefence secretary and the armed forces
OL,9,Fminister over military funding.
OL,11,FFurthermore, he could face a
OL,12,Fleadership challenge if Andy Burnham
OL,13,Fsucceeds in his bid to return to
OL,14,FWestminster in this week's Makerfield
OL,15,Fby-election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
