CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FAn ITV News investigation finds that
OL,7,Ftens of thousands of children across
OL,8,Fthe UK targeted on Snapchat, with
OL,9,Foffences including rape and sexual
OL,10,Fassault, as UK Editor Paul Brand
OL,11,Freports - Warning: Distressing content
OL,13,FTory shadow education secretary Laura
OL,14,FTrott said: "It's shameful that it's
OL,15,Ftaken the prime minister's job to be
OL,16,Fon the line for the government to
OL,17,Ffinally U-turn and ban social media
OL,18,Ffor under 16s.
OL,26,@vD@MOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31010
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,F"Three times Labour voted against a
OL,7,Fban, failing to stand up to Big Tech
OL,8,Fand protect children from the extreme
OL,9,Fcontent they are exposed to every day.
OL,11,F"As Conservatives we did not give up,
OL,12,FI kept fighting for the brave bereaved
OL,13,Fparents, health professionals, and
OL,14,Fcampaigners who continued to make the
OL,15,Fcase for change. This victory belongs
OL,16,Fto them.
OL,18,F"The Conservatives in opposition can
OL,19,Fmake a difference and this change will
OL,20,Ffinally help parents and protect
OL,21,Fchildhood."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31011
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FLord Nash, a Tory former education
OL,7,Fminister who led the campaign for an
OL,8,Funder-16s social media ban in the
OL,9,FHouse of Lords, said: "The government
OL,10,Fnow has an opportunity to draw a line
OL,11,Fin the sand and end tech companies'
OL,12,Funcontrolled experiment with
OL,13,Fchildren's safety.
OL,15,F"They must deliver in full on their
OL,16,Fpledge to raise the age limit to 16
OL,17,Ffor harmful platforms and features,
OL,18,Fwith robust age verification to ensure
OL,19,Fit is properly enforced.
OL,26,@qD@WOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31012
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,F"Only by doing this can they begin to
OL,7,Fend the catastrophic harm being done
OL,8,Fto a generation. Let's give our
OL,9,Fchildren their childhood back."
OL,11,FBut some groups have argued that a ban
OL,12,Fmay not be the appropriate instrument
OL,13,Fto tackle a wide spread of social
OL,14,Fmedia harms.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31013
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FThe Molly Rose Foundation, set up in
OL,7,Fmemory of 14-year-old Molly Russell,
OL,8,Fwho took her own life in 2017 after
OL,9,Fviewing harmful content online, said a
OL,10,Fsocial media ban "will fail to tackle
OL,11,Ffundamental product safety risks
OL,12,Fissues and leaves parents with a false
OL,13,Fsense of safety".
OL,15,FChief executive Andy Burrows said: "A
OL,16,Fmajority of children will continue to
OL,17,Fuse high-risk sites that will have no
OL,18,Fincentive to implement robust
OL,19,Fprotections.
OL,26,@rD@ROUuD@PO]wD@dOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31014
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,F"This is not what online safety
OL,7,Fexperts believe will work and is
OL,8,Fnecessary. Keir Starmer has chosen to
OL,9,Fabdicate responsibility for tackling
OL,10,Fharmful algorithms and his legacy will
OL,11,Fbe setting back children's safety by
OL,12,Fyears."
OL,14,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
