OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31015
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,FThe co-chairwoman of the All-Party
OL,7,FParliamentary Group for digital
OL,8,Fcreators, Labour's Feryal Clark,
OL,9,Fargued young people should not lose
OL,10,Faccess to good-quality content that
OL,11,Fhelps young people learn and find
OL,12,Fcommunities.
OL,14,FShe said: "High-quality, creator-led
OL,15,Feducational video content is a
OL,16,Fcritical public resource and is not
OL,17,Fthe same thing as social media.
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31016
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781570085
OL,3,CUK expected to introduce social media
OL,4,Cban for under-16s
OL,6,F"For example, many young people use it
OL,7,Fto revise for GCSEs, to learn a
OL,8,Flanguage or a musical instrument. Any
OL,9,Flegislative intervention must capably
OL,10,Faddress this distinction.
OL,12,F"Failing to do so would be dangerously
OL,13,Fshort-sighted and cut off
OL,14,Fopportunities from young people at
OL,15,Fexactly the moment they need these
OL,16,Fthings most."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUxD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
